-sm font-medium rounded-t-lg transition-colors bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-600 hover:bg-neutral-200\">T</button><button class=\"px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-t-lg transition-colors bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-600 hover:bg-neutral-200\">U</button><button class=\"px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-t-lg transition-colors bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-600 hover:bg-neutral-200\">V</button><button class=\"px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-t-lg transition-colors bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-600 hover:bg-neutral-200\">W</button><button class=\"px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-t-lg transition-colors bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-600 hover:bg-neutral-200\">X</button><button class=\"px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-t-lg transition-colors bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-600 hover:bg-neutral-200\">Y</button><button class=\"px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-t-lg transition-colors bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-600 hover:bg-neutral-200\">Z</button></div><div class=\"h-1 bg-primary\"></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6\"><div class=\"block\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">A</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-500 italic\">No drugs or supplements found starting with this letter. Please add content in the Wagtail CMS admin.</p></div><div class=\"hidden\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">B</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-500 italic\">No drugs or supplements found starting with this letter. Please add content in the Wagtail CMS admin.</p></div><div class=\"hidden\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">C</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-500 italic\">No drugs or supplements found starting with this letter. Please add content in the Wagtail CMS admin.</p></div><div class=\"hidden\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">D</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-500 italic\">No drugs or supplements found starting with this letter. Please add content in the Wagtail CMS admin.</p></div><div class=\"hidden\"><h2 class=