.</p></div><div class=\"hidden\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">N</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-500 italic\">No drugs or supplements found starting with this letter. Please add content in the Wagtail CMS admin.</p></div><div class=\"hidden\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">O</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-500 italic\">No drugs or supplements found starting with this letter. Please add content in the Wagtail CMS admin.</p></div><div class=\"hidden\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">P</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-500 italic\">No drugs or supplements found starting with this letter. Please add content in the Wagtail CMS admin.</p></div><div class=\"hidden\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">Q</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-500 italic\">No drugs or supplements found starting with this letter. Please add content in the Wagtail CMS admin.</p></div><div class=\"hidden\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">R</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-500 italic\">No drugs or supplements found starting with this letter. Please add content in the Wagtail CMS admin.</p></div><div class=\"hidden\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">S</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-500 italic\">No drugs or supplements found starting with this letter. Please add content in the Wagtail CMS admin.</p></div><div class=\"hidden\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">T</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-500 italic\">No drugs or supplements found starting with this letter. Please add content in the Wagtail CMS admin.</p></div><div class=\"hidden\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">U</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-500 italic\">No drugs or supplements found starting with this letter. Please add content in the Wagtail CMS admin.</p></div><div class=\"hidden\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">V</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-500 italic\">No drugs or supplements found starting with this letter. Please add content in the Wagtail CMS admin.</p></div><div class=\"hidden\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">W</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-500 italic\">No drugs or supplements found starting with this letter. Please add content in the Wagtail CMS admin.</p></div><div class=\"hidden\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">X</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-500 italic\">No drugs or supplements found starting with this letter. Please add content in the Wagtail CMS admin.</p></div><div class=\"hidden\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">Y</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-500 italic\">No drugs or supplements found starting with this letter. Please add content in the Wagtail CMS admin.</p></div><div class=\"hidden\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">Z</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-500 italic\">No drugs or supplements found starting with this letter. Please add content in the Wagtail CMS admin.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">Understanding Medications</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-600 mb-4\">Medications are substances used to diagnose, cure, treat, or prevent disease. They can be prescription or over-the-counter.</p><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-2\">Important to Know</h3><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-neutral-700\"><li>Follow your healthcare provider&#x27;s instructions for taking medications</li><li>Be aware of potential side effects and interactions</li><li>Inform your provider about all medications you&#x27;re taking, including OTC products</li><li>Store medications properly according to instructions</li><li>Dispose of unused medications safely</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">Dietary Supplements</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-600 mb-4\">Dietary supplements include vitamins, minerals, herbs, amino acids, and other substances intended to supplement the diet.</p><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-2\">Important to Know</h3><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-neutral-700\"><li>Supplements are not intended to treat, diagnose, prevent, or cure diseases</li><li>Some supplements can interact with medications</li><li>Not all supplements have been tested for safety or effectiveness</li><li>Natural doesn&#x27;t always mean safe</li><li>Consult with your healthcare provider before taking supplements</li></ul></div></div></div></main><footer class=\"bg-neutral-100 pt-12 pb-6\"><div class=\"container-custom\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8\"><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-4\">About HealthInfo</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a class=\"text-neutral-600 hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/about\">About Us</a></li><li><a class=\"text-neutral-600 hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/editorial-policy\">Editorial Policy</a></li><li><a class=\"text-neutral-600 hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy Policy</a></li><li><a class=\"text-neutral-600 hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/terms\">Terms of Use</a></li><li><a class=\"text-neutral-600 hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/disclaimer\">Medical Disclaimer</a></li><li><a class=\"text-neutral-600 hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/about-ads\">Advertising Policy</a></li><li><a class=\"text-neutral-600 hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/contact\">Contact Us</a></li></ul></div><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-4\">Quick Links</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/conditions\">Conditions A-Z</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/drugs-supplements\">Drugs &amp; Supplements</a></li><li><a class=\"hover: